						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone in front of the temple of Hanumān.</hi></p>						

						<p>This damaged hero-stone seems to record the death of <hi rend="bold">Paḍevaḷa Eṟeyamma</hi> and a grant of land made in his memory. The characters belong to the <hi rend="bold">10-11th century A.D.</hi></p>						

